OL,3,C'Cold-blooded killer' jailed for 21
OL,4,Cyears for murder of mother-of-two
OL,6,FA "cold-blooded killer" who was
OL,7,Fextradited from Belgium after fatally
OL,8,Fstrangling a sex worker in a drug-
OL,9,Ffuelled attack has been jailed for 21
OL,10,Fyears for her murder.
OL,12,FAdam Watson killed mother-of two
OL,13,FSamantha Holden, 56, at her home in
OL,14,FFarnborough, Hampshire, on September
OL,15,F9, 2022, before fleeing the country
OL,16,Flater that day.
