OL,3,C'Cold-blooded killer' jailed for 21
OL,4,Cyears for murder of mother-of-two
OL,6,FThe 37-year-old from Farnborough was
OL,7,Fstopped and arrested the following day
OL,8,Fand was extradited for Ms Holden's
OL,9,Fmurder and also to complete his period
OL,10,Fof licence for a previous sexual
OL,11,Fassault offence in 2014.
OL,13,FA CPS spokesman said: "Watson was a
OL,14,Fclient of Ms Holden, who was a sex
OL,15,Fworker and saw clients at her home
OL,16,Faddress.
OL,18,F"Her body was discovered by her son a
OL,19,Ffew hours after the event.
