OL,3,C'Cold-blooded killer' jailed for 21
OL,4,Cyears for murder of mother-of-two
OL,6,F"In court, it was heard that Watson
OL,7,Fwas identified as the last person to
OL,8,Fcontact Ms Holden through her phone
OL,9,Frecords.
OL,11,F"He denied murder, instead claiming
OL,12,Fthat he acted in self-defence.
OL,14,F"However, prosecutors with CPS Wessex
OL,15,Funravelled his lies to the jury,
OL,16,Fpiecing together the pathologist's
OL,17,Freport and DNA evidence to prove that
OL,18,FWatson was the aggressor.
OL,26,@sD@AOUvD@AOU
