OL,3,C'Cold-blooded killer' jailed for 21
OL,4,Cyears for murder of mother-of-two
OL,6,F"His DNA was found underneath Ms
OL,7,FHolden's fingernails, around her neck,
OL,8,Fand on the cushion used to suffocate
OL,9,Fher. Watson was found with scratch
OL,10,Fmarks from where Ms Holden fought for
OL,11,Fher life."
OL,13,FRuth Sands, a Senior Crown Prosecutor
OL,14,Fwith CPS Wessex, said: "Adam Watson is
OL,15,Fa cold-blooded killer who attempted to
OL,16,Fevade justice by fleeing the country,
OL,17,Fwhilst his victim still lay
OL,18,Fundiscovered.
