OL,3,C'Cold-blooded killer' jailed for 21
OL,4,Cyears for murder of mother-of-two
OL,6,F"Despite his considerable effort to
OL,7,Fcircumvent the consequences of his
OL,8,Fdeplorable actions, the CPS, working
OL,9,Fwith the NCA, was able to secure his
OL,10,Fextradition from Belgium so that he
OL,11,Fcould come back and face justice, and
OL,12,Fwe are grateful to the Belgian
OL,13,Fauthorities for their assistance.
OL,15,F"We also worked closely with Hampshire
OL,16,FConstabulary, whose meticulous
OL,17,Finvestigation work greatly aided our
OL,18,Fability to deliver swift justice.
OL,26,@nD@AOUwD@AOU
