OL,3,C'Cold-blooded killer' jailed for 21
OL,4,Cyears for murder of mother-of-two
OL,6,F"I want to pay tribute to the strength
OL,7,Fof Samantha's family. They have
OL,8,Fexperienced things no family should,
OL,9,Fand I hope that this sentence can
OL,10,Fbegin to close this awful chapter for
OL,11,Fthem."
OL,13,FIn a statement released through
OL,14,FHampshire police, Ms Holden's family
OL,15,Fsaid: "My family and I are relieved
OL,16,Fthat there is now justice for our
OL,17,Fbeautiful mum.
OL,19,F"We love her and miss her very much
OL,20,Fand now we can move forward with her
OL,21,Fin our hearts."
