OL,6,FDetective Inspector Howard Broadribb
OL,7,Fadded: "Our thoughts, first and
OL,8,Fforemost, are with the friends and
OL,9,Ffamily of Samantha Holden.
OL,11,F"Not only have her family had to
OL,12,Fendure what happened that day, but
OL,13,Fthey have had to relive their
OL,14,Fexperience in court.
OL,16,F"This was a senseless and horrific
OL,17,Fincident which resulted in a much-
OL,18,Floved mum losing her life.
