OL,6,F"I would like to praise Samantha's
OL,7,Ffamily and children for their bravery,
OL,8,Fcourage and assistance when they were
OL,9,Fdealing with unimaginable pain and
OL,10,Fgrief having just lost their mum.
OL,12,F"I hope that today's sentence helps
OL,13,Fthem to rebuild their lives and that
OL,14,Fthey are able to feel a small sense of
OL,15,Fcomfort that justice has been
OL,16,Fdelivered.
